te";s:19:"2017-03-02 14:48:50";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-03-02 11:48:50";s:12:"post_content";s:5538:"<div class="page-header">\r\n<h2>LDT - Production of spring tines (double torsion springs) up to 12,00 mm</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align="left">The LDT line consist of two machines. LDT DT machine is used for production of spring tines (double torsion springs) from bended wire forms which are made on LDT OBL machine. These machines can be used as a single machine or in the line.</p>\r\n<p align="center"><a title="Fortuna Federn Vimeo Channel" href="https://vimeo.com/channels/fortunafedern" target="_blank">\r\nVisit our Fortuna Federn Vimeo channel to see all our available videos!</a>Click on the picture to enlarge it!</p>\r\n<p align="center"><a href="http://www.fortunafedern.com/cms/index.php/en/online-anfrageformular?view=form">Use our online form to send us your inquiry directly from here.</a></p>\r\n<p align="left">LDT DT machine is used for coiling of spring tines (double torsion springs) from bended wire forms which are made on LDT OBL machine (see below).</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Type</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>LDT DT-6</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>LDT DT-12</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Spring steel wire range acc. to\r\nEN 10270-1 DH ph</td>\r\n<td align="center">3,00 - 6,00 mm\r\n<em>.118" - .236"</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">6,00 - 12,00\r\n<em>.236" - .472"</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Min. spring OD</td>\r\n<td align="center">15,00 mm\r\n<em>.590"</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">30,00 mm\r\n<em>1.181"</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Productivity (pieces/hour)</td>\r\n<td align="center">cca. 400</td>\r\n<td align="center">cca. 300</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Drive</td>\r\n<td align="center">2 x servo</td>\r\n<td align="center">4 x servo</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Mandrel positioning</td>\r\n<td align="center">pneumatic</td>\r\n<td align="center">servo</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Accessories (included in the price)</td>\r\n<td align="center">1 set of tooling\r\nacc. to the client\'s requirment</td>\r\n<td align="center">1 set of tooling\r\nacc. to the client\'s requirment</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Software</td>\r\n<td align="center">German / English</td>\r\n<td align="center">German / English</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Dimensions LxWxH cca.</td>\r\n<td align="center">120 x 80 x 120 cm\r\n<em>3.94 x 2.62 x 3.94 feet</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">135 x 88 x 120 cm\r\n<em>4.43 x 2.89 x 3.94 feet</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Weight cca.</td>\r\n<td align="center">600 kg\r\n<em>1,350 pounds</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">800 kg\r\n<em>1,750 pounds</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="left"></p>\r\n<p align="left">LDT OBL machine is used for wire straightening (from the wire coil) and than for production of bended wire forms which are than used for making spring tines (double torsion springs) on LDT DT machine (see above). The feeding unit consists of wire straightener (3 segments) and 2 pairs (3 pairs on OBL-12) of feeding rolls. The cutting is done by one hydraulic cylinder and the bending is done by another hydraulic cylinder (on request even more). it is necessary to use the power reel (see <a title="HMV - power reels with load capacity up to 2,400 kg" href="http://www.fortunafedern.com/cms/index.php/en/maschinen/hmv" target="_blank">HMV</a>) in order to guarantee the accuracy.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Modell</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>LDT OBL-6\r\n</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>LDT OBL-12\r\n</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Spring steel wire range acc. to\r\nEN 10270-1 DH p</td>\r\n<td align="center">3,00 - 6,00 mm\r\n<em>.118" - .236"</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">6,00 - 12,00 mm\r\n<em>.236" - .472"</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Feeding speed</td>\r\n<td align="center">80 meters/min\r\n<em>262 feet/min</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">65 meters/min\r\n<em>213 feet/min</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Productivity (pieces/hour)</td>\r\n<td align="center">ca. 600</td>\r\n<td align="center">ca. 500</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Drive</td>\r\n<td align="center">1 x servo</td>\r\n<td align="center">1 x servo</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Number of feeding rolls</td>\r\n<td align="center">2 pairs</td>\r\n<td align="center">3 pairs</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Hydraulic power unit</td>\r\n<td align="center">included</td>\r\n<td align="center">included</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Accessories (included in the price)</td>\r\n<td align="center">1 set of tooling\r\nacc. to the client\'s requirment</td>\r\n<td align="center">1 set of tooling\r\nacc. to the client\'s requirment</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Software</td>\r\n<td align="center">German / English</td>\r\n<td align="center">German / English</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Dimensions LxWxH cca.</td>\r\n<td align="center">400 x 200 x 260 cm\r\n<em>13.12 x 6.56 x 8.53 feet</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">500 x 200 x 260 cm\r\n<em>16.40 x 6.56 x 8.53 feet</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Weight cca.</td>\r\n<td align="center">1.700 kg\r\n<em>3,700 pounds</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">2.000 kg\r\n<em>4,409 pounds</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="center"><a title="Fortuna Federn Vimeo Channel" href="https://vimeo.com/channels/fortunafedern" target="_blank">Visit our Fortuna Federn Vimeo channel to see all our available videos!</a></p>\r\n<p align="center"><a href="http://www.fortunafedern.com/cms/index.php/en/online-anfrageformular?view=form">Use our online form to send us your inquiry directly from here.</a></p>\r\n<p align="center">You cannot find what you are looking for? No probelm! Visit our <a title="Custom build section" href="http://www.fortunafedern.com/cms/index.php/en/machinery/custom-build">custom build section</a>!</p>";s:10:"post_title";s:3:"LDT";s:12:"post_excerpt"