ly. Through combination of up to 8 separate bending segments with variable speed adjustment you are able to work very efficiently.\r\n<p align="center"><a title="Fortuna Federn Vimeo Channel" href="https://vimeo.com/channels/fortunafedern" target="_blank">\r\nVisit our Fortuna Federn Vimeo channel to see all our available videos!</a>Click on the picture to enlarge it!</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Type</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>BEM-12</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>BEM-14</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>BEM-16</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Wire diameter range\r\nacc. to EN 10270-1 DH ph (ASTM A228)</td>\r\n<td align="center">4,00 - 12,00 mm*\r\n<em>.157" - .472"*</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">5,00 - 14,00 mm*\r\n<em>.197" - .551"*</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">6,00 - 16,00 mm*\r\n<em>.236" - .629"*</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Max. wire diameter\r\nof soft wire (p.E. 50CrV4)</td>\r\n<td align="center">15,00 mm*<em>\r\n.590"*</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">18,00 mm*<em>\r\n.708"*</em></td>\r\n<td align="center">22,00 mm*<em>\r\n.866"*</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Productivity</td>\r\n<td align="center">ca. 1.000 bendings\r\n(360°) / hour</td>\r\n<td align="center">ca. 600 bendings\r\n(360°) / hour</td>\r\n<td align="center">ca. 600 bendings\r\n(360°) / hour</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Drive</td>\r\n<td align="center">Servo - 4,00 kW</td>\r\n<td align="center">Servo - 5,00 kW</td>\r\n<td align="center">Servo - 8,00 kW</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Accessories incl. in the price</td>\r\n<td align="center">various tooling</td>\r\n<td align="center">various tooling</td>\r\n<td align="center">various tooling</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="center">* depends of the bending radius</p>\r\nHere you can see sample application with custom made tooling:\r\n<p align="center">* the double torsion spring (spring tine) has been made on our <a title="LDT Produktseite" href="http://www.fortunafedern.com/cms/index.php/en/maschinen/ldt">LDT OBL-12 and LDT DT-12</a>!</p>\r\n<p align="center"><a href="http://www.fortunafedern.com/cms/index.php/en/online-anfrageformular">Use our inquiry form directly here on our website.</a></p>\r\n<p align="center">You cannot find what you are looking for? No probelm! Visit our <a title="Custom build section" href="http://www.fortunafedern.com/cms/index.php/en/machinery/custom-build">custom build section</a>!</p>";s:10:"post_title";s:7:"BEM CNC";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:423:"BEM CNC half automatic servo controlled CNC wire bending machine is designed for very easy and fast production of bending parts from wire (strip with additional accessories on request). The control is very easy and with foot switch (on request only) you can start each bending action very easily. Through combination of up to 8 separate bending segments with variable speed adjustment you are able to work very efficiently.";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:9:"bem-cnc-2";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-03-02 14:42:47";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-03-02 11:42:47";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:43:"http://fortunafedern-new/product/bem-cnc-2/";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:7:"product";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:9;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:131;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-03-02 14:41:32";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-03-02 11:41:32";s:12:"post_content";s:2834:"<div class="page-header">\r\n<h2>BEM CNC - Drahtbiegemaschinen bis 16,00 mm</h2>\r\n</div>\r\nBEM CNC halbautomatische servo gesteuerte Drahtbiegemaschinen eignen sich zum Fertigen von unterschiedlichsten Biegeteilen aus Draht (Band mit spez. Werkzeugen auf Anfrage). Die Bedienung ist sehr einfach und mittels Fußtaste (nur auf Anfrage) können Sie jede Biegeaktion einfach starten. Durch die Kombination von bis zu 8 verschiedenen Biegesegmenten mit variabler Geschwindigkeit sind Sie in der Lage sehr effizient zu arbeiten.\r\n<p align="center"><strong><a title="Fortuna Federn Vimeo Channel" href="https://vimeo.com/channels/fortunafedern" target="_blank">\r\nBesuchen Sie unseren Fortuna Federn Vimeo Kanal, um die verfügbaren Videos unserer Maschinen zu sehen!</a></strong>Klicken Sie auf das jeweilige Bild, um es zu vergrössern!</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Type</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>BEM-12</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>BEM-14</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>BEM-16</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Drahtdurchmesserbereich\r\nlt. EN 10270-1 DH ph</td>\r\n<td align="center">4,00 - 12,00 mm*</td>\r\n<td align="center">5,00 - 14,00 mm*</td>\r\n<td align="center">6,00 - 16,00 mm*</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Max. Drahtdurchmesser von\r\nweichem Draht (z.B. 50CrV4)</td>\r\n<td align="center">15,00 mm*</td>\r\n<td align="center">18,00 mm*</td>\r\n<td align="center">22,00 mm*</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Produktivität</td>\r\n<td align="center">ca. 1.000 Biegungen\r\n(360°) / Stunde</td>\r\n<td align="center">ca. 600 Biegungen\r\n(360°) / Stunde</td>\r\n<td align="center">ca. 600 Biegungen\r\n(360°) / Stunde</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Antrieb</td>\r\n<td align="center">Servo - 4,00 kW</td>\r\n<td align="center">Servo - 5,00 kW</td>\r\n<td align="center">Servo - 8,00 kW</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Zubehör im Preis enthalten</td>\r\n<td align="center">div. Werkzeuge</td>\r\n<td align="center">div. Werkzeuge</td>\r\n<td align="center">div. Werkzeuge</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="center">* immer vom Biegeradius abhängig\r\n\r\nHier ein Anwendungsbeispiel mit Sonderzubehör (wurde auf Kundenwunsch gefertigt):</p>\r\n<p align="center"